PASTEL SMOKES drifted on the cabaret\rquote s air. Each smoke, the signature of a table, wafted upward from a table\rquote s central vent\emdash here a pale mauve, across the way a pink as delicate as b
aby skin, there a green that brought to mind Indian gauze woven of pampas grass. It had just turned 9:00 P.M. and the }{\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 Cabaret A\rquote Chigua}{
\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 , Bahia\rquote s finest, had begun its nightly entertainment. Tinkling bell music set a sensuous rhythm for a troupe of dancers posturing in stylized ant costumes. 
Their fake antennae and mandibles waved through the smokes.
\par }{\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 A\rquote Chigua\rquote s}{\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183  patrons occupied low divans. 
The women were a sprinkling of tropical color as rich as jungle flowers arranged against men in white linen and, here and there like punctuation marks, the glistening white smocks of bandeirantes. 
This was the Green area, where bandeirantes could relax and play after duty in the Red jungle or at the barriers.
\par Shoptalk and smalltalk in a dozen languages flowed through the room\emdash 
\par \'93Tonight I take a pink table for luck. It is the color of a woman\rquote s breast, no?\'94 \'93So I laid down a blanket of foamal and we went in and cleaned out the whole nest\emdash mutated ants like they had in the Piratininga. Must\rquote 
ve been ten, twenty billion of them right there.\'94
\par Dr. Rhin Kelly had listened to the room for twenty minutes, her attention drawn more and more to the tension undercurrents here.
\par \'93The new poisons work\emdash yes.\'94 That was a bandeirante at the table behind her answering the problem of survivors\emdash resistant strains. \'93The mop-up is going to be brutal handwork, just like China. 
They had to get down there and kill the last bugs by hand.\'94
\par Rhin sensed her companion stirring, and thought: }{\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 He heard}{\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 . She glanced up from their table\rquote 
s amber smoke, met her escort\rquote s almond eyes. He smiled, and she thought as she had many times before, what a distinguished }{\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 personage}{
\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183  was this Dr. Travis Huntington Chen-Lhu. He was tall with the deep, square face of North China topped by close-cropped hair that was still jet-black at sixty. 
He leaned toward her and whispered, \'93Nowhere do we escape rumors, eh?\'94
\par She shook her head, wondering for perhaps the tenth time why the distinguished Dr. Chen-Lhu, district director for the International Ecological Organization, had insisted she come here tonight, her first night in Bahia. 
She had no illusions at all about why he\rquote d ordered her to come down from Dublin: he obviously had a problem which required action by the IEO\rquote s espionage arm. As usual, the problem would turn out to involve a man who must be manipulated. 
Chen-Lhu had hinted as much during the day\rquote s \'93general briefing.\'94 But he had yet to name the man upon whom she must ply her wiles.
\par \'93They say certain plants are dying out from lack of pollenization.\'94 That was a woman at the table behind her, and Rhin stiffened. Dangerous conversation, that.
\par But the bandeirante directly behind her said, \'93Back off, doll. You sound like that dame they picked up in Itabuna.\'94
\par \'93What }{\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 dame}{\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 ?\'94
\par \'93She was distributing Carsonite literature right there in the village behind the barrier. Police grabbed her before she\rquote d gotten rid of twenty pieces. They got most of it back, but you know how that stuff is, especially up there near the Red.
\'94
\par A disturbance erupted at }{\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 A\rquote Chigua\rquote s}{\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183  entrance, cries of \'93Johnny! You, Johnny! You lu
cky dog, Joao!\'94
\par Rhin joined the rest of }{\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 A\rquote Chigua\rquote s}{\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 
