\par \'93That there has been some sort of tragedy at the waterfront and again at the Monte Ochoa Convent and orphanage.\'94
\par \'93What sort of tragedy?\'94
\par \'93That is what Rhin\rquote s investigating.\'94
\par \'93You saw that out there on the lawn,\'94 Martinho said. \'93Now will you believe what we\rquote ve been reporting to you these many months?\'94
\par \'93I saw an acid-shooting automaton and a man in the costume of a stag beetle,\'94 Chen-Lhu said. \'93I\rquote m curious to know if you were party to this deception.\'94
