\par \'93Easy, Padre,\'94 Alvarez said. \'93The stories never say. It\rquote s always }{\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 they}{\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183  or }{
