\par \'93I am going over now and look in that hole,\'94 Martinho said.
\par Alvarez reached out, took Vierho\rquote s carbine. He hung it on his good shoulder by the sling, took the control handle of the shield. \'93I will go with you, Johnny.\'94
\par Martinho glanced at Vierho, saw the look of terrified relief in the man\rquote s face, returned his attention to Alvarez. \'93Your arm?\'94
