\par \'93Travis, you stay close behind us,\'94 Martinho said.
\par \'93My Security men have just arrived,\'94 Chen-Lhu said. \'93Delay a moment and we\rquote ll ring that place. I will tell them to bring shields.\'94
\par \'93It is wise, Johnny,\'94 Alvarez said.
\par \'93We will go slowly,\'94 Martinho said. \'93Padre, return to the truck. Tell Ramon to bring it around the Plaza and up onto the edge of the lawn over there. Have the Hermosillo truck direct all its lights onto that place.\'94 He nodded ahead of him.

