\par \'93Chen-Lhu hinted at this,\'94 Martinho said.
\par \'93Is this not the place?\'94 Alvarez asked.
\par \'93Stop the shield,\'94 Martinho said. He stared at the grass ahead of them, searching out the place\emdash the relationship to the fountain, the grass marked by the previous passage of their shield.
