\par \'93Padre, down here,\'94 he whispered.
\par Vierho leaned over him with the carbine. \'93Jefe?\'94
\par \'93Just ahead of the bar\emdash into the ground.\'94
\par Vierho aimed, squeezed off two shots.
\par A violent scrabbling noise erupted under the lawn ahead of them. Something splashed there.
\par Again, Vierho fired. The blast pellets made a curious thumping sound as they exploded under the ground.
\par There came the liquid sound of furious activity down there\emdash as though there was a school of fish feeding at the surface.
