\par \'93Where could we go?\'94 he asked.
\par \'93This violence appears to be local,\'94 Chen-Lhu said. He paused, listening: the mob sounds had grown louder. \'93Go to your father\rquote s place in Cuiaba. Take your band with you. The others can go to your bases in the Red.\'94
\par \'93Why must I\'85\'94
\par \'93I will send Rhin to you when we\rquote ve devised a plan of action.\'94
\par \'93I must know where to find you,\'94 Rhin said, picking up her cue. And she thought: }{\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 The father\rquote s place, yes. That must be the center of it\'85
