\par \'93But we\rquote ve done nothing,\'94 Martinho said.
\par \'93Please,\'94 she said.
\par Vierho tugged his arm.
\par Martinho took a deep breath. \'93Padre, go with the men. It\rquote ll be safer out there in the Red. I\rquote ll take the small truck and go to Cuiaba. I must discuss this with my father, the Prefect. 
