\par }{\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 The voice\emdash that rasping, stridulant sound}{\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 . 
Again, Joao asked himself how the creature could produce that simulation of human speech. The coordination required for that action had profound implications.
\par Joao looked out to his left. The moon was high overhead now, illuminating the line of bandeirante towers off there. The first barrier.
\par The truck would be out of the Green soon and into the Gray of the poorest Resettlement Plan farms\emdash then, beyond that, another barrier and the Gre
at Red that stretched in reaching fingers through the Goyaz and the inner Mato Grosso, far out to the Andes where teams were coming down from Ecuador. Joao could see scattered lights of Resettlement Plan farms ahead, darkness beyond.
\par The airtruck was going faster than he wanted, but Joao knew he dared not slow it. They might become suspicious.
\par \'93You must go higher,\'94 said the creature behind him.
\par Joao increased pump displacement, raised the nose. He leveled off at three hundred meters.
\par More bandeirante towers loomed ahead, spaced at closer intervals. Joao picked up the barrier signals on his dash meters, looked back at his guard. The dissembler vibrations of the barrier seemed to have no effect on the creature.
\par Joao looked out his side window and down as they passed over the barrier. No one down there would challenge him, he knew. This was a bandeirante airtruck headed into the Red\'85 and with its transmitter sending out a homing call. 
The men down there would assume he was a band leader headed out on contract after a successful bid, calling his men to him for the job. If the barrier guards recognized his call wave, that would only confirm the thought.
\par Joao Martinho had just completed a successful bid on the Serra dos Parecis. All the bandeirantes knew that.
\par Joao sighed. He could see the moon-silvered snake of the Sao Francisco winding off to his left, and the lesser waterways like threads raveled out of the foothills.
\par }{\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 I must find the nest\emdash wherever we\rquote re headed}{\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 , Joao thought.
\par He wondered if he dared turn on his receiver\emdash but if his men started reporting in\'85 No. That would make the creatures suspect; they might take violent counter-action.
\par }{\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 My men will realize something\rquote s wrong when I don\rquote t answer}{\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 , he thought. }{
\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 They\rquote ll follow}{\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 .
\par }{\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 If any of them hear my call}{\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 .
\par \'93How far are we going?\'94 Joao asked.
\par \'93Very far,\'94 the guard said.
\par Joao settled himself for a long trip. }{\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 I must be patient}{\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 , he thought. }{
\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 I must be as patient as a spider waiting beside her web}{\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 .
\par Hours droned past: two, three\'85 four.
\par Nothing but moonlighted jungle sped beneath the truck, and the moon lay low on the horizon, near setting. This was the deep Red where broadcast poisons had been used at first with near disastrous results. 
This was where the first wild mutations had been discovered.
\par The Goyaz.
\par }{\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 This is where my father said Rhin Kelly went}{\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 , Joao thought. }{
