\par That, for sure.
\par This would be an expensive flight\emdash unless it had already been lost.
\par }{\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 I mustn\rquote t think that way}{\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 , Joao told himself. }{
