\par IEO maps showed this region in varied intensities of red. Around the red ran a ring of gray with pink shading where one or two persistent forms of insect life resisted man\rquote s poisons, jelly flames, astringents, sonitoxics\emdash 
the combination of flamant couroq and supersonics that drove insects from their hiding places into waiting death\emdash and all the mechanical traps and luring baits in the bandeirante arsenal.
\par A grid map would be placed over this area and each thousand-hectare square offered for bid to the independent bands to deinfest.
\par }{\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 We bandeirantes are a kind of ultimate predator}{\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 , Joao thought. }{
