\par He rolled over and over, eyes tightly closed, feeling the insect bites like fire needles over every exposed part of his body. Hands grabbed him and he felt a jelly hood splash across his face to protect it. Hard spray slammed against him from all sides.

\par Somewhere in a hood-blurred distance he heard a voice that sounded like Vierho\rquote s shout, \'93Run! This way\emdash run!\'94
\par He heard a spraygun fire: }{\i\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 Whoosh!}{\cf1\lang1033\langfe1049\langnp1033\insrsid15279183\charrsid15279183 
