THE REPORT, although interesting for its variations, added little to the Brain\rquote 
s general information about humans. They reacted with shock and fear to the display along the river bank. That was to be expected. The Chinese had demonstrated practicality not shared by the other two. This fact, added to the appa
rent attempts of the Chinese to get the other two to mate\emdash that might be significant. Time would tell.
