\par The Brain\rquote s sensors reviewed once more the messenger pattern being repeated on the cavern ceiling.
\par The vehicle was approaching a series of rapids. Its occupants could be killed there and irrevocably lost. Or they might renew their efforts to fly away in the craft. There lay a worry-element requiring a heavy weighing factor.
