\par Chen-Lhu stared downriver across the front seats, watching the moon-path crawl beneath the pod. The path rippled with spider lines in the eddies, flowed like painted silk in the broad reaches.
\par The breathing sounds of deep, satiated sleep came from the front of the cabin.
\par }{\i\cf1\insrsid15279183 Now I probably will not have to kill that fool, Johnny}{\cf1\insrsid15279183 , Chen-Lhu thought.
