\par }{\i\cf1\insrsid15279183 He is dead, Johnny\rquote s companion}{\cf1\insrsid15279183 , Chen-Lhu thought. }{\i\cf1\insrsid15279183 That was a simulacrum we saw beside the river. Nothing could\rquote 
