\par }{\i\cf1\insrsid15279183 A bootless question}{\cf1\insrsid15279183 .
\par Rhin turned in her sleep, pressed close to Joao. \'93Mmmmm,\'94 she murmured.
\par }{\i\cf1\insrsid15279183 Our friends will not hold off the attack much longer}{\cf1\insrsid15279183 , Chen-Lhu thought. }{\i\cf1\insrsid15279183 It\rquote s obvious they\rquote ve just been awaiting the proper time and place. Where will it come\emdash 
