\par \'93Are you sure it\rquote s a truck?\'94 Rhin asked. \'93Perhaps\'85\'94
\par \'93Bandeirante truck,\'94 Joao said. \'93They\rquote ve rigged it to fire alternate pairs and save fuel. Hear that? That\rquote s a bandeirante trick.\'94
\par \'93Could they be searching for us?\'94
\par \'93Who knows? Anyway, they\rquote re above the clouds.\'94
\par \'93And above our friends, too,\'94 Chen-Lhu said.
\par The pulsating counterpoint of rocket motors echoed along the hills. Joao turned his head to follow the sound. It grew fainter upstream, blended with the lapping-swishing-tumbling of the river.
\par \'93Won\rquote t they come down and look for us?\'94 Rhin pleaded.
\par \'93They weren\rquote t looking for anyone,\'94 Joao said. \'93They were just going from someplace to someplace.\'94
