\par \'93We could shoot them down!\'94 she said. She reached for a sprayrifle, but Joao grabbed her arm, stopped her.
\par \'93There\rquote re still the clouds,\'94 he said.
\par \'93And our friends have more reinforcements than we have spray charges,\'94 Chen-Lhu said. \'93That I\rquote ll wager.\'94
\par \'93But if the clouds weren\rquote t there,\'94 she said. \'93Won\rquote t the clouds ever\'85 go away?\'94
