\par \'93They\rquote re gone,\'94 Rhin said.
\par \'93That only means the truck is no longer with us,\'94 Joao said.
\par Rhin buried her face in her hands, fought down shuddering sobs.
\par Joao started to caress her neck, to comfort her, but she shook off his hand.
\par And Chen-Lhu thought: }{\i\cf1\insrsid15279183 You must attract him, Rhin, not repel him}{\cf1\insrsid15279183 .
\par \'93We must remember why we are here,\'94 Chen-Lhu said. \'93We must remember what it is we must do.\'94
\par Rhin sat up, lowering her hands, took a deep breath that hurt the muscles of her chest.
\par \'93We must keep ourselves occupied,\'94 Chen-Lhu said. \'93With trivia if necessary. It is a way to prevent\'85 fear, boredom, angers. I tell you\emdash I will describe for you an orgy I once attended in Cambodia. There
