 but if the man held back, conserved those energies\'85
\par \'93Do you think you understand me, Johnny?\'94 Chen-Lhu asked.
\par \'93No, I don\rquote t understand you.\'94
\par \'93Really, I\rquote m quite uncomplicated; it\rquote s not difficult to understand me,\'94 Chen-Lhu said.
\par \'93That\rquote s one of the most complicated statements any man ever made,\'94 Joao said.
\par \'93Do you mock me?\'94 Chen-Lhu asked, and he put down an upsurge of dismay and anger. Johnny was acting most out of character.
\par \'93How could I mock if I don\rquote t understand?\'94 Joao asked.
\par \'93Something has come over you,\'94 Chen-Lhu said. \'93What is it? You are behaving most strangely.\'94
\par \'93Now we understand each other,\'94 Joao said.
\par }{\i\cf1\insrsid15279183 He goads me}{\cf1\insrsid15279183 , Chen-Lhu thought. }{\i\cf1\insrsid15279183 HE goads ME!}{\cf1\insrsid15279183  And he asked himself: }{\i\cf1\insrsid15279183 Will I have to kill this fool?}{\cf1\insrsid15279183 
\par \'93See how easy it is to keep busy and forget our troubles,\'94 Joao said.
