\par The pod floated backward down the river now, and Rhin stared upstream at hills that disappeared into drifting clouds. }{\i\cf1\insrsid15279183 Why do I bother with such questions?}{\cf1\insrsid15279183  she wondered. }{\i\cf1\insrsid15279183 We don
