\par And Chen-Lhu answered, \'93Ancestry is no longer important in my land, Rhin.\'94
\par The pump sucked air with a wet gurgling, the sound drowning Rhin\rquote s reply. Joao replaced the cap on the inspection hole, returned to the cabin.
