\par \'93Many women are beautiful,\'94 he said.
\par \'93One of those dark, full-breasted types, I\rquote ll bet,\'94 she said. \'93Have you had her to bed?\'94
\par And Joao thought: }{\i\cf1\insrsid15279183 What does this mean? That we\rquote re all bohemian types together?}{\cf1\insrsid15279183 
