\par \'93Weren\rquote t you ever human, Travis?\'94 Rhin asked. \'93Even for just a day or so?\'94
\par \'93Shut up!\'94 Chen-Lhu barked, and he sat back, astonished at himself. }{\i\cf1\insrsid15279183 The bitch! How did she get through to me like that?}{\cf1\insrsid15279183 
\par }{\i\cf1\insrsid15279183 Ahhh}{\cf1\insrsid15279183 , Joao thought, }{\i\cf1\insrsid15279183 she touched a nerve}{\cf1\insrsid15279183 .
\par \'93What made an animal out of you, Travis?\'94 Rhin asked.
